schools.name: Palm Bay Magnet Senior High School

data.description: Double lot in Palm Bay on sewer and city water!!   This home features 4 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, 1 car garage and a spacious 28x13 family room.   Look at this list of improvements, roof replacement 2022, air conditioner 2022, water heater 2021 and electrical panel in 2021.   Appliances are 2020 with a gas range.  The whole home has been re-plumbed in 2022 for years of worry free living.  Storage shed has new roof and plenty room for toys and extra storage.   Close access to highways, schools, restaurants and shopping too!
